03:31.254 --> 03:34.384
Security found herjust after 1:00.
Name's Molly Simms.

03:34.384 --> 03:36.600
She's a veterinarian in Bedford.

03:36.600 --> 03:37.932
She's in town for the horse show.

03:37.932 --> 03:39.125
She came from the party?

03:39.125 --> 03:41.883
A dinner for the horse folks.

03:41.883 --> 03:43.986
She was doing a bed check on the clients' horses.

03:43.986 --> 03:46.972
- McClintock?
- No. Madison.

03:47.948 --> 03:50.721
Uh, what killed the horses?

03:50.721 --> 03:54.519
Three-inch nails through the skull.
Found a nail gun in the stall.

03:54.519 --> 03:56.789
I'll get Mr. McClintock.

03:57.841 --> 03:59.932
She came to check on the Madison horse...

03:59.932 --> 04:03.998
and found somebody pumping 
nails into these horses.

04:09.169 --> 04:12.125
Yeah, see the way her legs are tucked under?

04:12.125 --> 04:15.564
She came in,
she saw the injured horses.

04:15.564 --> 04:19.365
It would have been her instinct 
to kneel down to help them.

